snippet.textDisplay: Great job, guys. But you guys have to understand that Coke Studio is listened to around the world, by people who don't understand our language. Every song must have top-level English subtitles accompanying it, so that foreigners can feel the full  impact of every song. Soft power projection is extremely vital in today's world. And music is one way to project our soft power. Hope that the music maestro and our pride, Xulfi, will take note.
